title: Chef Robotics launches its most advanced assembly robot yet
description:
Chef Robotics unveiled Chef+, an advanced AI robot with doubled capacity and a new automated meal flattening tool.

The post Chef Robotics launches its most advanced assembly robot yet appeared first on The Robot Report.
